abstract: Suicide attacks against security checkpoints and Shiite worshipers in Iraq kill at least 23 people.
lead_paragraph: Suicide attacks against security checkpoints and Shiite worshipers killed at least 23 people in Iraq on Thursday, officials said.
snippet: Suicide attacks against security checkpoints and Shiite worshipers killed at least 23 people in Iraq on Thursday, officials said.
